#Where Esha turns 22 ♥️

Hey there! We’re Ashi and Esha – best friends since our college days and forever foodies at heart. Together, we created “plate_for_two”, a space where we share our love for food, fun activities, and all things friendship!

This page is our little corner of the internet, built with laughter, memories, and the hope of creating a community filled with love, support, and lots of delicious recommendations.
Come be a part of our journey — we’d love to have you with us! Don’t forget to hit that follow button!
